snippet.title: Bryce Vine - La La Land ft. YG [Official Music Video]
snippet.description:
Watch the official music video for La La Land by Bryce Vine feat. YG from the album Carnival.
🔔 Subscribe to the channel: https://youtube.com/user/BryceVine?sub_confirmation=1

Listen to Carnival 🎪 here: https://brycevine.lnk.to/Carnival

Starring Bryce Vine, YG, and Melanie Iglesias
Director:  James Larese

Tiggy the English Bulldog was provided by Road Dogs & Rescue. They are a rescue in Los Angeles that focuses on French and English bulldogs and puppies born with birth defects ❤️ Bulldogs can have many health issues and special needs puppies are often euthanized at birth.
Road Dogs believes all dogs deserves a chance! 
Follow them on IG @roadogs and please donate to save more pups like Tiggy here: http://www.roadogsandrescue.org/donate/

Follow Bryce Vine:
Facebook: http://facebook.com/brycevine​
Twitter: https://twitter.com/brycevine​
Instagram: https://instagram.com/brycevine

Bryce Vine is a rapper-singer renowned for his hit songs "Drew Barrymore," "La La Land," "I'm Not Alright," "The Fall," "Classic and Perfect," "Sunflower Seeds," and "Guilty Pleasure." He worked with artists like Wale, YG, and Loud Luxury — amassing billions of global streams and receiving multi-platinum certifications.
